item.title: Ferry Magic Family
item.author: jsacosta1103@gmail.com (Jerad Acosta)
item.description: Wednesday night, January 15 around 4:30pm I was watching a cloud strum show put on by The Game Master, The Pirate Ship, Astronaughts, The Dream Liner, and the Black Whole New World. Toward the end I saw a family of four come out in the eye of a giant moving statue. The Father Mother and two children, Daughter's around 8 wearing a tuo-tuo and around 12. All posed and asked me to take a photograph - they called to me by name.
